<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=yes">
    <title>Crush² 搜索引擎 | 权威学术 vs 垃圾屎坑</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: system-ui, 'Segoe UI', 'Comic Neue', 'Poppins', 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #fff0f5 0%, #ffe4ec 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        /* 主容器 */
        .crush-engine {
            max-width: 1000px;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
            border-radius: 3rem;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 45px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 105, 180, 0.3);
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        /* 头部无厘头区域 */
        .hero {
            background: #ffb7c5;
            padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 6px dashed #ff6f91;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            color: #2d1b2e;
            text-shadow: 3px 3px 0 #ffdf6b;
            word-break: keep-all;
        }

        .hero h1 span {
            display: inline-block;
            transform: rotate(4deg);
            background: #fff2b5;
            padding: 0 12px;
            border-radius: 60px;
        }

        .tagline {
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-top: 8px;
            color: #4a2a3a;
            font-weight: 600;
            background: #fff0d6;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.3rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 40px;
        }

        /* 搜索框区域 */
        .search-area {
            padding: 2rem 2rem 1rem;
            background: #fff9fc;
        }

        .input-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 100px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            border: 1px solid #ffbfcf;
            padding: 5px;
        }

        .input-group input {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            border: none;
            outline: none;
            background: transparent;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #2d1b2e;
        }

        .input-group input::placeholder {
            color: #ff9ab3;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .input-group button {
            background: #ff8aa8;
            border: none;
            padding: 0 2rem;
            border-radius: 60px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.2s;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .input-group button:hover {
            background: #ff6a8e;
            transform: scale(0.97);
        }

        /* 模式切换 Toggle 双雄 */
        .mode-toggler {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .mode-btn {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0.9rem 0.5rem;
            border-radius: 60px;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            background: #f2e3e8;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            transition: all 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.2, 1.2, 0.8, 1);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 12px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .mode-btn.authority {
            background: #d9e8ff;
            color: #0057b3;
            border-color: #a0c4ff;
        }

        .mode-btn.shit {
            background: #ffe0c4;
            color: #a55217;
            border-color: #ffb882;
        }

        .mode-btn.active {
            transform: scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .mode-btn.authority.active {
            background: #2a6fdb;
            color: white;
            border-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px #ffb7c5;
        }

        .mode-btn.shit.active {
            background: #c96f0e;
            color: #fff3e0;
            border-color: #ffd966;
        }

        /* 搜索结果容器 */
        .results-container {
            padding: 1rem 2rem 2rem;
            background: #fffbfd;
            border-top: 2px dotted #ffccd9;
        }

        .result-stats {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: baseline;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .badge-mode {
            background: #ffe0e7;
            padding: 0.3rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .warning-shit {
            background: #f7d44a;
            color: #5e2a00;
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 0.2rem 0.9rem;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .result-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        /* 通用卡片风格 */
        .result-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 28px;
            padding: 1.3rem 1.5rem;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
            border-left: 12px solid;
        }

        /* 权威卡片 */
        .authority-card {
            border-left-color: #2a6fdb;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, #f7f9ff);
        }
        .authority-card .card-title {
            color: #1f509e;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        .citation-meta {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: #4b6e9e;
            margin: 6px 0;
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        /* 垃圾卡片 —— 完全污染风格 */
        .shit-card {
            border-left-color: #e68a2e;
            background: #fff6ea;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(232, 120, 0, 0.15);
        }
        .shit-card .card-title {
            color: #b45f1b;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        .shit-source {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            background: #ffe2c1;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 2px 10px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-family: monospace;
            margin-top: 6px;
        }

        .snippet {
            margin: 10px 0;
            line-height: 1.45;
            color: #2c2c2c;
        }

        .footer-note {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: #bc8f9f;
            border-top: 1px dashed #ffcddb;
            padding-top: 1.2rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 650px) {
            body {
                padding: 1rem;
            }
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 1.7rem;
            }
            .mode-btn {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
                gap: 6px;
            }
            .input-group button {
                padding: 0 1rem;
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
            .results-container {
                padding: 1rem;
            }
        }

        button {
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .random-suggestion {
            background: none;
            border: none;
            color: #ff88aa;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            text-decoration: underline;
            margin-left: 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="crush-engine">
    <div class="hero">
        <h1>
            💘 CRUSH² 引擎 💩
            <span>权威✨ vs 屎坑🤡</span>
